videos.description: Baylor guard Jared Butler bounces the ball to forward Freddie Gillespie, who rises up to throw down a dunk with his left hand.

videos.description: Baylor forward Freddie Gillespie rises up to grab an offensive rebound while surrounded by defenders and banks in the bucket while drawing contact.
